Amber Heard is an American actress. She is also a model. Amber Heard is one of the most beautiful women in the world. She is regarded as a sex symbol. She is always listed amongst the most beautiful and sexiest women in the world. Her notable films include Never Back Down, The Rum Diary, Pineapple Express and Drive Angry.

Amber Heard was born on April 22, 1986. She was born in Austin, Texas. She was born to Patricia Paige and David Clinton Heard. She has a sister named Whitney. Amber Heard dropped out of high school. She eventually got her diploma from homeschooling. She declared herself atheist after reading Ayn Rand’s Work. Her first movies role was in Friday Night Lights. She then had a small role in the film Alpha Dog.

She starred in the film All Boys Want Mandy Lane in 2006. Her role alongside Sean Faris in the action film Never Back Down was her breakthrough performance. By 2007 Amber Heard was a popular actress. She is always considered among the sexiest women in the world. In 2010, she starred in Drive Angry with Nicolas Cage. She also starred in The Rum Diary with Johnny Depp. She also starred in the movie Syrup. She had a cameo role in Machete Kills. She also starred in 3 Days to kill, a French American crime thriller. She will star in the upcoming films London Fields, When I Live My Life Over Again and The Danish Girl.

Amber Heard is openly bisexual. She came out in 2010. She dated photographer Tasya van Ree. She met actor Johnny Depp one the sets of The Rum Diary. They started dating in 2012. The couple got married in a private ceremony on February 3, 2015. She is rated as one of the sexiest women in the world. HSe was ranked 10th on Maxim’s hot 100 in 2010.
